      "text": "A 70-year-old woman is being evaluated for monoclonal gammopathy. Bone marrow examination showed abnormal proliferation of plasma cells with evidence of certain microscopic features. Match the following structures with corresponding histopathological images regarding this condition. 1. Flame Cell a) 2. Mott cell b) 3. Russel bodies c) 4. Dutcher bodies d)",
